OL,3,CBan new, young drivers from carrying
OL,4,Cpassengers of similar age ` AA
OL,6,FThese measures would be a form of
OL,7,Fgraduated driving licensing (GDL),
OL,8,Fwhich is used in several countries,
OL,9,Fincluding the US, Canada, Australia
OL,10,Fand Sweden.
OL,12,FThe AA estimated that introducing GDL
OL,13,Fin the UK would save at least 58 lives
OL,14,Fand prevent 934 people being seriously
OL,15,Finjured in road crashes each year.
OL,17,FDepartment for Transport (DfT) figures
OL,18,Fshow 290 people were killed and 4,669
OL,19,Fwere seriously injured in crashes on
OL,20,FBritain's roads last year involving at
OL,21,Fleast one driver aged 17-24.
