OL,6,F"We are calling on the Transport
OL,7,FSecretary to make simple, pragmatic
OL,8,Fchanges to the licensing process so
OL,9,Fyoung people are better protected in
OL,10,Ftheir first few months of independent
OL,11,Fdriving."
OL,13,FUnder the Conservative government, the
OL,14,FDfT announced in July 2019 it was
OL,15,Fconsidering introducing GDL in
OL,16,FEngland, but the assessment was halted
OL,17,Fin autumn 2020, partly because of the
OL,18,Fpotential impact on young people's
OL,19,Femployment.
