OL,6,FThe most popular element of the AA's
OL,7,Fproposal, according to an online
OL,8,Fsurvey of 10,566 of its members, was
OL,9,Fpassenger restrictions, with 33% of
OL,10,Frespondents saying they would support
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,FEdmund King, director of the AA
OL,14,FCharitable Trust, said: "The
OL,15,Fintroduction of passenger restrictions
OL,16,Fwould help mitigate the increased risk
OL,17,Fyoung drivers have to manage when they
OL,18,Fhave peer-aged passengers travelling
OL,19,Fwith them.
