OL,6,F"A six-month restriction is a small
OL,7,Fprice to pay for saving young lives.
OL,9,F"There is a great swell of support for
OL,10,Fthe introduction of GDL so this
OL,11,FGovernment has a real opportunity to
OL,12,Fmake it happen and save lives.
OL,14,F"The very recent inquest into the
OL,15,Ftragic deaths of four young men is a
OL,16,Fstark reminder that action needs to be
OL,17,Ftaken to protect young lives, and it
OL,18,Fneeds to be taken sooner rather than
OL,19,Flater."
