OL,6,FLast week, senior coroner for north-
OL,7,Fwest Wales Kate Robertson raised
OL,8,Fconcerns about young, newly qualified
OL,9,Fdrivers carrying passengers after an
OL,10,Finquest into the deaths of four
OL,11,Fteenagers who drowned when their car
OL,12,Frolled into a ditch in November last
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FA DfT spokesperson said: "Every death
OL,16,Fon our roads is a tragedy and our
OL,17,Fthoughts remain with the families of
OL,18,Feveryone who has lost a loved one in
OL,19,Fthis way.
